The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for question answering, which are typically covered in the arXiv categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves graph-based representations of text, which are relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
